    Closed --> [*]

    note right of Unbound
        Created via no-arg constructor or SocketImpl constructor.
        bind() must be called before accept().
        setReceiveBufferSize() and setPerformancePreferences()
        must be called before bind() to take full effect.
    end note

    note right of Bound
        Created via port-based constructors or after bind().
        bind() throws IOException if called again (already bound).
        accept() blocks until a connection is made.
    end note

    note right of Closed
        Terminal state. close() is idempotent.
        setOption/getOption throw IOException when closed.
        setReuseAddress throws SocketException when closed.
    end note
